message: "If you use this repository, please cite it as an active research repository at an intermediate methodological stage."
title: "Quantum–Spacetime Bridge"
abstract: >-
  A cautious, wave-based research framework exploring whether weighted
  relational structure can provide a bounded methodological bridge between
  quantum organization and spacetime-related effective structure. The current
  repository documents an intermediate research stage and should not be read as
  a completed theory claim.
